Description: ==============
        play cassandra
        ==============
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/play_cassandra.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/play_cassandra
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/davidemoro/play_cassandra.svg?branch=develop
