        =======
        CHANGES
        =======
        
        0.0.4 (2019-01-25)
        ------------------
        
        - Supports new pytest-play >= 2.0 YAML based syntax (json no more supported)
        
        
        0.0.3 (2018-01-23)
        ------------------
        
        - speed up cassandra connections with cache
        
        
        0.0.2 (2018-01-22)
        ------------------
        
        - removed play_python from dependencies (deprecated)
        
        
        0.0.1 (2018-01-16)
        ------------------
        
        * First release
        
